Subject: Needle Felting 201 - Description Errata
Description: A follow up to Needle Felting 101 panel. Learn to felt 3D objects! Tools and material provided to create a cute little friend. Use of sharp needles; children over 12 welcome with parental supervision.  If you are unable to attend, there will be some extra take-home kits available with self guided instructions, so stop by and have a POKE! Space is limited, so please sign up near Ops!  Speakers include:Liz 'Smoothie' DeBruyn - Track: DIY  - Duration: 1 hour
